{
  "info": {
    "name": "Concert Ticket Booking — GEEK Up Assessment",
    "_postman_id": "geekup-concert-booking-2026",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Concert Ticket Booking Platform.\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Set `baseUrl` variable = `http://localhost:8080`\n2. Run **Login as Customer** → token auto-saved to `customerToken`\n3. Run **Login as Operator** → token auto-saved to `operatorToken`\n4. Run **Login as Admin** → token auto-saved to `adminToken`\n5. Use any endpoint — auth headers are pre-configured per folder.\n\n## Seeded Test Accounts (password: `password123`)\n- `admin@geekup.vn` → ADMIN\n- `operator1@geekup.vn` → OPERATOR\n- `customer1@test.com` → CUSTOMER\n- `customer2@test.com` → CUSTOMER\n\n## Seeded Data (IDs after Flyway migration)\n- Concert 1: AIGHT FLASH SALE CONCERT 2026 (PUBLISHED)\n- Concert 2: HANOIFEST 2026 (PUBLISHED)\n- Concert 3: UPCOMING SHOW — DRAFT\n- Category 1: SVIP — 2,500,000đ (Concert 1, max 2/booking)\n- Category 2: VIP — 1,500,000đ (Concert 1, max 4/booking)\n- Category 3: Standard — 800,000đ (Concert 1, max 4/booking)\n- Category 4: VIP — 1,200,000đ (Concert 2)\n- Category 5: Standard — 600,000đ (Concert 2)\n- Voucher `FLASHSALE10`: 10% off, min order 500,000đ\n- Voucher `VIP200K`: 200,000đ off, min order 1,500,000đ\n- Voucher `EXPIRED2025`: expired (use to test 400)\n- Voucher `INACTIVE_TEST`: inactive (use to test 400)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",       "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customerToken", "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "operatorToken", "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken",    "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "concertId",     "value": "1",                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "draftConcertId","value": "3",                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryId",    "value": "2",                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "bookingId",     "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "idempotencyKey","value": "",                      "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 0. Auth",
      "description": "Register & login. Login scripts auto-save tokens to collection variables.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Register New Customer",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"newuser@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"fullName\": \"New User Test\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('success = true', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.success).to.be.true;",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login as Customer (customer1)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"customer1@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Token present', () => pm.expect(body.data.token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "if (body.success && body.data && body.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', body.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('✅ customerToken saved');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login as Operator",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"operator1@geekup.vn\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.success && body.data && body.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('operatorToken', body.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('✅ operatorToken saved');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login as Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@geekup.vn\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.success && body.data && body.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', body.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('✅ adminToken saved');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login — Wrong Password (expect 401)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"customer1@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"wrongpassword\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 401 Unauthorized', () => pm.response.to.have.status(401));",
                  "pm.test('success = false', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.success).to.be.false;",
                  "    pm.expect(body.errorCode).to.equal('INVALID_CREDENTIALS');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "🎵 1. Public — Concerts",
      "description": "No authentication required.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "List Published Concerts",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/concerts?page=0&size=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api","v1","concerts"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "10" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Returns PUBLISHED concerts only', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.content).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Get Concert Detail (ID=1 Flash Sale)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/concerts/{{concertId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","concerts","{{concertId}}"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Concert is PUBLISHED', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.status).to.equal('PUBLISHED');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Get Concert Ticket Categories (ID=1)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/concerts/{{concertId}}/categories", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","concerts","{{concertId}}","categories"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Returns at least one category', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data).to.be.an('array').with.length.above(0);",
                  "    if (body.data.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('categoryId', String(body.data[0].id));",
                  "    }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "name": "Get Concert Detail — Not Found (expect 404)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/concerts/9999", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","concerts","9999"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 404 Not Found', () => pm.response.to.have.status(404));",
                  "pm.test('errorCode = CONCERT_NOT_FOUND', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.errorCode).to.equal('CONCERT_NOT_FOUND');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "🎟️ 2. Customer — Bookings",
      "description": "Requires Bearer {{customerToken}}. Run Login as Customer first.",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{customerToken}}", "type": "string" }]
      },
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — VIP Ticket (no voucher)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Auto-generate a fresh UUID for idempotency key each run",
                  "const uuid = require('uuid');",
                  "const key = pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}');",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotencyKey', key);",
                  "console.log('idempotencyKey:', key);"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Booking status = PENDING', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.status).to.equal('PENDING');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('bookingId', String(body.data.id));",
                  "    console.log('✅ bookingId saved:', body.data.id);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 2,\n      \"quantity\": 2\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — VIP + Standard (multi-category)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotencyKey', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Booking has 2 items', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.items).to.have.length(2);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 2,\n      \"quantity\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 3,\n      \"quantity\": 2\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — With Voucher FLASHSALE10",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotencyKey', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Discount applied', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.finalAmount).to.be.below(body.data.totalAmount);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 3,\n      \"quantity\": 2\n    }\n  ],\n  \"voucherCode\": \"FLASHSALE10\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — With Voucher VIP200K",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotencyKey', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Fixed discount = 200000', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.discountAmount).to.equal(200000);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 2,\n      \"quantity\": 1\n    }\n  ],\n  \"voucherCode\": \"VIP200K\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — Idempotency Retry (same key, expect 200 cached)",
          "description": "Gửi lại request với cùng X-Idempotency-Key từ lần trước → phải nhận lại response giống hệt (HTTP 200, không tạo booking mới).",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK (cached, not 201)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Returns same bookingId', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const savedId = pm.collectionVariables.get('bookingId');",
                  "    pm.expect(String(body.data.id)).to.equal(savedId);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 2,\n      \"quantity\": 2\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — Exceed maxPerBooking (expect 400)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotencyKey', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 400 Bad Request', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
                  "pm.test('TICKET_QUANTITY_EXCEEDED', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().errorCode).to.equal('TICKET_QUANTITY_EXCEEDED');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 1,\n      \"quantity\": 5\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — Cross-concert items (expect 400)",
          "description": "Mix items từ concert 1 (categoryId=2) và concert 2 (categoryId=4) trong 1 đơn → BOOKING_CROSS_CONCERT",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotencyKey', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 400 Bad Request', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
                  "pm.test('BOOKING_CROSS_CONCERT', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().errorCode).to.equal('BOOKING_CROSS_CONCERT');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 2,\n      \"quantity\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 4,\n      \"quantity\": 1\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — Expired Voucher (expect 400)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotencyKey', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 400 Bad Request', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
                  "pm.test('VOUCHER_EXPIRED', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().errorCode).to.equal('VOUCHER_EXPIRED');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",      "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotencyKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 3,\n      \"quantity\": 1\n    }\n  ],\n  \"voucherCode\": \"EXPIRED2025\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Create Booking — No Idempotency Key (expect 400)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 400 Bad Request', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"ticketCategoryId\": 2,\n      \"quantity\": 1\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Get My Bookings (paginated)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Returns paged list', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.content).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.totalElements).to.be.a('number');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings?page=0&size=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api","v1","bookings"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "10" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Get Booking Detail",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Booking belongs to current user', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.data.id).to.equal(Number(pm.collectionVariables.get('bookingId')));",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
